channel.title: Neighborhood Watch Bypass :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Objective Difficulty Description 1/5 Assist Kyle at the old data center with a fire alarm that just won’t chill. Kyle Parrish mission statement If you spot a fire, let me know! I’m Kyle, and I’ve been around the Holiday Hack Challenge scene for years as arnydo - picked up multiple Super Honorable Mentions along the way. When I’m not fighting fires or hunting vulnerabilities, you’ll find me on a unicycle or juggling - I once showed up a professional clown with his own clubs!
